a673dd5ac9d0ed4ea5359f22c3ac9294cdd9a5d6.query:
SELECT
                            id::text AS "id!: String",
                            (
                                CASE kind
                                    WHEN 'webinar' THEN 'webinars'
                                    WHEN 'classroom' THEN 'classrooms'
                                    ELSE ''
                                END
                            ) AS "kind!: String"
                        FROM class
                        WHERE event_room_id = $1
                            OR original_event_room_id = $1
                            OR modified_event_room_id = $1
                        UNION ALL
                        SELECT
                            id::text AS "id!: String",
                            'chats' AS kind
                        FROM chat
                        WHERE event_room_id = $1
